Model Specific Description: This field is used to indicate an identifier attributed to the documented built work.
This field is used to indicate the type of an identifier attributed to the documented built work.
This field is used to indicate the institution providing the documented built work it's ID.
This field is used to indicate the source based on which the identifier was attributed to the object.
This field is used to indicate the main name attributed to the documented instance of built work.
This field is used to indicate the language of the name attributed to the documented built work.
This field is used to indicate the formal type of the documented built work.

This field is used to indicate additional names under which the documented instance of built work is known. This can be linked to the additional name type and earliest and latest date of use of that name.
This field is used to indicate the type of alternative name that is attributed to the documented instance of built work.
This field is used to indicate the language of the alternative name attributed to the documented built work.
This field is used to indicate the earliest known date for use of an alternative name for the documented instance of built work.
This field is used to indicate the latest known date for use of an alternative name for the documented instance of built work.
This field is used to indicate the organization or individual attributing the alternative name to the documented built work.
This field is used to associate the documented instance of built work to a style which it can be classified with or for which it is exemplary.
This field is used to associate the documented instance of built work to a style which it can be classified with or for which it is exemplary.
